---
// Footer.astro - 页脚组件
---

<footer class="py-12 px-4 border-t border-claude-border">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <!-- 左侧信息 -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-claude-primary to-claude-secondary">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">
          Agent Skills Guide - 让 Claude 学会你的工作方式
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- 右侧链接 -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Ekko7778/claude-skills-guide"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/build-with-claude/agent-skills"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors"
        >
          官方文档
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
